[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1230","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1230.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1022","title":"SGI IRIX serial_ports 程序 PATH 环境变量信任本地权限提升漏洞","description":"SGI IRIX 4.x 与 5.x 系统中的 serial_ports 管理程序在运行时信任用户自定义的 PATH 环境变量来查找并执行 ls 程序，未做路径校验。本地已登录的低权限用户可在 PATH 中植入伪造的特制 ls 程序（特洛伊木马），当 serial_ports 以 root 权限调用 ls 时便会执行该恶意程序，从而提升至 root 权限。该漏洞影响 SGI IRIX 4.x 及 5.2/5.3 等版本，攻击需本地账户访问权限，利用门槛低、危害为本地提权。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":6.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1022"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1994-10-02T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:32.487","remediation":"建议升级到已修复该问题的 SGI IRIX 6.2 或更高版本，并安装 SGI 官方安全补丁（如 1999 年发布的相应补丁集）。在无法立即升级时，应以 root 身份将 serial_ports 程序中的 ls 调用路径改为绝对路径 /bin/ls，并收紧该程序 setuid 权限或限制普通用户执行权限，同时检查并清理用户环境中可疑的 PATH 值与伪造的 ls 程序作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-19T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/archive/1/930","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/464","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/2111","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19351","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/7e65fa522cff0172990568230ff9b719b8650296/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1022.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1022","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/1fe9b156eeeb72b8f8baa50bbe7bc0d9806e8c64/content/CVE-1999-1022.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/7aedbd0209e609a1924ad29a8dda684737576137/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1022.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/5d945305f2cad48b7bb06af582393a58c31555d3/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-29g7-m78g-3fx6/GHSA-29g7-m78g-3fx6.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1310.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154600_154700.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000058.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/63d4031680b3d3fa77b826660a1e30ffc70ff5cd/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1022.json","https://github.com/Yuning-J/VulnerabilityClassifier/blob/c0f06c21b73c26b5ee2b75c21a498eb04eada4b5/threatPrediction/cveIDThreatType/cve_idgainpre"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1230.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1419","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1419.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1238","title":"HP HP-UX CORE-DIAG Fileset 本地权限提升漏洞","description":"HP-UX 9.05 及之前版本的 CORE-DIAG 文件集中的 HP message catalog 存在权限管理缺陷，本地攻击者可通过利用该组件对消息目录文件的不当权限配置，获取超出自身授权范围的系统权限，实现本地权限提升。该漏洞影响 HP-UX 9.05 及更早版本，CVSS 评分 4.6，攻击者需具备本地访问权限，无需身份认证即可利用。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1238"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1994-09-21T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:00.780","remediation":"升级 HP-UX 至 10.0 或更高版本，该漏洞已在后续版本中修复。如无法升级，以 root 身份执行 `swmodify -x fileset_only=false CORE-DIAG` 移除该 fileset，或通过 `chmod 700 /usr/sbin/diag/` 限制 CORE-DIAG 目录仅 root 可访问以降低本地非授权用户利用风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/advisories/1531","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/2262"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1419.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1257","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1257.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1219","title":"SGI IRIX sgihelp 本地权限提升漏洞","description":"SGI IRIX 操作系统 5.2 及更早版本（含 5.1）内置的 sgihelp 帮助系统及打印管理器存在本地权限提升漏洞。由于相关程序（可能通过 clogin 命令）在处理过程中未正确限制特权操作，导致本地普通用户可利用该程序获取 root 超级用户权限。该漏洞影响范围限于运行上述版本 IRIX 的本地系统，攻击条件为攻击者需先获得目标主机的本地登录权限。利用方式为本地用户执行或触发 sgihelp 相关组件，借助其缺陷提升自身权限至 root，进而完全控制系统。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1219"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1994-08-11T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:58.367","remediation":"建议将 SGI IRIX 系统升级至受支持的 IRIX 6.5 或更高版本以修复此漏洞。临时缓解措施包括：以 root 身份移除 sgihelp 和 clogin 命令的 setuid 位（执行 chmod u-s /usr/sbin/sgihelp /usr/bin/clogin），禁止普通用户执行这些程序；同时通过 /etc/passwd 和 /etc/group 严格限制系统账户权限，并检查 /var/adm/SYSLOG 中是否有本地提权攻击痕迹。由于 IRIX 5.x 已完全停止支持，长期方案应迁移至现代操作系统。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-19T00:00:00Z","references":["http://ciac.llnl.gov/ciac/bulletins/e-33.shtml","http://www.cert.org/advisories/CA-1994-13.html","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/468","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/511","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19354","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/2aa0c2dcb1730150467a1bc57cd9b2ece96310af/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1219.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1219","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/1fe9b156eeeb72b8f8baa50bbe7bc0d9806e8c64/content/CVE-1999-1219.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/d7bfe9c86213fdf5ad56116fa46ee20a047ec9da/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1219.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/ce77465efdf58fc31a7a0bc8c83705be48abcedf/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-66gj-m4p3-m782/GHSA-66gj-m4p3-m782.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x1000/468/info.html","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1219.json","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_3.list.dict","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000055.txt","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--29102abf-cbfc-4c27-9009-657d6b974762.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-1257.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1257.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1420","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1420.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1239","title":"HP HP-UX Xauthority 本地授权绕过漏洞","description":"HP-UX 9.x 操作系统的 Xauthority 认证机制在特定条件下未能正确启用，导致本地用户即使未经显式授权也能访问 X 显示服务。该漏洞源于 X11 窗口系统的权限控制缺陷，攻击者只需拥有本地系统访问权限即可利用，无需特殊权限。成功利用后可获取其他用户的 X 显示内容，造成敏感信息泄露。HP 已发布相关安全公告修复此问题。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1239"],"sources":["cve","avd"],"published":"1994-07-13","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"升级 HP-UX 系统至 10.x 及以上版本，该版本完整支持 Xauthority 认证机制。如无法升级，可通过编辑 /etc/dt/config/Xservers 文件启用访问控制（加上 -nolisten tcp 参数），并使用 xhost 限制仅授权用户可访问 X 显示。同时确保用户主目录下的 .Xauthority 文件权限为 600。建议迁移至受支持的操作系统版本。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/advisories/1559","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/2261"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1420.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0393","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0393.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0207","title":"Majordomo 邮件列表管理 lists 命令远程执行漏洞","description":"Majordomo 1.89/1.90 及更早版本存在命令执行漏洞。远程攻击者可通过向邮件列表服务器发送特制邮件，在 Reply-To 字段中嵌入恶意 \"lists\" 命令参数，利用该漏洞在目标系统上以邮件服务器进程权限执行任意命令。该漏洞影响广泛部署的 Majordomo 邮件列表管理软件，攻击者无需认证即可远程触发，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高危。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0207"],"sources":["cve","exploitdb"],"published":"1994-06-09","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"升级 Majordomo 至 1.94 或更高版本，该版本已修复通过 Reply-To 字段注入 lists 命令参数的远程命令执行漏洞。若无法升级，应在 wrappers 配置中限制 lists 命令执行权限，并严格过滤邮件头中特殊字符。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0207","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/20597"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0393.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0393.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0556","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0556.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0337","title":"IBM AIX batch queue (bsh) 本地和远程权限提升漏洞","description":"IBM AIX 操作系统的批处理队列（bsh）存在权限提升漏洞。当网络打印服务启用时，本地或远程攻击者可通过向批处理队列提交特制任务，利用不充分的权限控制机制获取超出授权的系统访问权限，导致攻击者能够执行任意命令或操作。该漏洞影响早期版本的 AIX 系统，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0337"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1994-06-03T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:10.850","remediation":"立即安装 IBM 针对 AIX batch queue (bsh) 的安全补丁，升级到 AIX 4.3.3 及更高修复版本。如无法打补丁，可通过 `chsubserver -r bsh` 禁用 bsh 网络打印服务，或在 `/etc/security/user` 中限制 bsh 可执行权限仅为 root 用户。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0337","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/b8581edcbd9fb1606112c43470d0a7cb92a751f8/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0337.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0337","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0337.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/0fec8c5c64ee33c93da01ddd0b28bf8f9f743a61/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0337.json","https://github.com/stg-tud/cveenhance/blob/6476e73d87cdc9cf610342ef15d131432ab41588/Annotations/Wollny/CVE-1999-0337.xml","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/3f4ce19e2c9952be92df5da9390e93383644298b/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-r76x-g7v4-r3c6/GHSA-r76x-g7v4-r3c6.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0337.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154600_154700.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000050.txt","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--6dd5b793-7342-42d5-867d-37abc515d322.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0556.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0660","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0660.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0423","title":"HP HP-UX hpterm 本地权限提升漏洞","description":"HP-UX 10.20 系统中的 hpterm 终端模拟器存在权限提升漏洞，本地攻击者可通过向 hpterm 发送特制请求利用该漏洞，从而获取额外的系统权限。该漏洞需要攻击者拥有本地访问权限，利用条件相对有限，影响 HP-UX 10.20 系统，CVSS 评分 4.6，危害等级中危。建议升级到不受影响的版本或应用厂商发布的安全补丁。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0423"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1994-06-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:21.910","remediation":"建议升级至 HP-UX 11.0 及以上版本，或安装 HP 发布的 PHSS_19011 补丁。如无法升级，执行 `chmod 755 /usr/bin/hpterm` 移除 hpterm 的 setuid 位，或通过 `chmod 0` 禁用该程序作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www1.itrc.hp.com/service/cki/docDisplay.do?docId=HPSBUX9903-093"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0660.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0256","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0256.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0113","title":"IBM AIX rlogin 权限提升漏洞","description":"IBM AIX 3.2.5 的 rlogin 实现中存在参数注入漏洞（CWE-88），当向 rlogin 命令传入 `-froot` 参数时，未经授权的本地攻击者可利用该参数绕过正常的身份认证机制，以 root 权限直接登录目标系统，实现权限提升。该漏洞源于程序未对命令行参数进行有效过滤和消毒，攻击者无需知道目标用户密码即可获取系统最高控制权。该漏洞影响 IBM AIX 3.2.5 版本，CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0113"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1994-05-23T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:36.820","remediation":"建议立即升级 IBM AIX 至 4.1.0 及以上版本（该漏洞已在 AIX 4.x 中修复），或安装对应 APAR 补丁。同时禁用 rlogin/rsh/r-commands 系列服务（注释 /etc/inetd.conf 中相关行并重启 inetd），迁移至 OpenSSH 替代远程管理。限制 root 远程登录，在 /etc/securetty 中移除不必要的终端，并启用 PAM 认证机制。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/458","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19348","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/297eb115816d3735806f02ee33bb4d2d53ecd5c6/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0113.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0113","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0113.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0113.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2ed73314b4d66512efbb22e0644e615bc00001f2/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0113.json","https://github.com/eldondev/Snort/blob/34bdcf6a7a638b55c7c04f77ef1efa526ad08e33/doc/signatures/604.txt","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/nessus/nessus-plugins/scripts/rlogin_froot.nasl","https://github.com/bailehang/snort_2.2.0/blob/34f8a3a85f15645aea53d6e0d46863c7c57e43ef/doc/signatures/609.txt","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/murahari1/recon-tool/blob/f63a205225373d0d87b081758c11899777970b0f/README.md"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0256.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1348","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1348.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1134","title":"HP Vue 本地权限提升漏洞","description":"HP Vue 3.0 图形用户界面环境存在权限提升漏洞，本地攻击者可通过利用 Vue 组件中的缺陷获取 root 权限。该漏洞影响 HP 9.x 系列操作系统，攻击者需拥有本地系统访问权限方可利用，无需身份认证即可提权至超级用户。HP 已发布补丁 PHSS_4038、PHSS_4055 和 PHSS_4066 修复此问题。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1134"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1994-05-18T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:47.570","remediation":"立即安装 HP 发布的补丁 PHSS_4038、PHSS_4055 和 PHSS_4066，升级 Vue 3.0 至修复版本。如无法打补丁，应限制本地用户对 Vue 程序的执行权限，移除不必要的 setuid 位，并禁用 guest 账户作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-19T00:00:00Z","references":["http://ciac.llnl.gov/ciac/bulletins/e-23.shtml","http://packetstorm.securify.com/advisories/hpalert/008","http://www.iss.net/security_center/static/2284.php","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/aa3114da1227373bef7855dba21bcaa5f0e0ad76/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1134.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1134","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/1fe9b156eeeb72b8f8baa50bbe7bc0d9806e8c64/content/CVE-1999-1134.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/b4ddb28f94d250449ab64c1617f45b1f91701fa2/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1134.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/bf2339193e1c10dc2db330718adeb8cc8d88c4dd/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-5rw3-h39w-p5j4/GHSA-5rw3-h39w-p5j4.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x88000/87952/info.html","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/134977c5f4ce4f427a914ca161b4f075e34b560b/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1134.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154600_154700.json","https://github.com/Yuning-J/VulnerabilityClassifier/blob/c0f06c21b73c26b5ee2b75c21a498eb04eada4b5/threatPrediction/cveIDThreatType/cve_idgainpre","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/112b6cf2eb30218e492a77c7d1bcb2220cd940b5/1999.tsv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1348.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0266","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0266.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0120","title":"Sun Solaris utmp 文件本地权限提升漏洞","description":"Sun Solaris 操作系统中 utmp 文件存在权限配置不当漏洞。当该文件被设置为非 root 用户可写时，本地攻击者可修改 utmp 文件内容，从而获取 root 权限。该漏洞影响 SunOS/Solaris 系统，需要攻击者拥有本地账户权限，攻击者可通过构造特制的 utmp 记录实现权限提升，危害等级高危。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0120"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1994-03-21T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:37.890","remediation":"确保 utmp 文件仅 root 可写：执行 `chmod 644 /var/adm/utmp` 或 `chmod 644 /etc/utmp` 移除其他用户的写权限，同时 `chown root:root /var/adm/utmp` 确保文件属主为 root。升级到已修复此问题的 SunOS/Solaris 安全补丁版本。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://sunsolve.sun.com/pub-cgi/retrieve.pl?doctype=coll&doc=secbull/126"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0266.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0557","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0557.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0338","title":"IBM AIX 性能工具本地权限提升漏洞","description":"AIX 操作系统的许可软件产品性能工具存在权限提升漏洞，本地攻击者可利用该工具集的特权配置缺陷，通过执行特定命令获取 root 权限。该漏洞影响 IBM AIX 多个版本，攻击者需要拥有本地系统访问权限即可利用，无需用户交互。成功利用后攻击者可完全控制系统，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0338"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1994-02-24T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:11.000","remediation":"安装 IBM 针对该漏洞发布的 AIX APAR 补丁包，或升级至包含该修复的最新 AIX 维护级别（Maintenance Level）。临时缓解措施：以 root 用户执行 `chmod u-s /usr/bin/filemon /usr/bin/svmon /usr/bin/tprof` 移除受影响性能工具的 setuid 权限，并限制非授信用户对性能工具目录的访问权限。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0338"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0557.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0397","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0397.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0211","title":"Sun Solaris NFS mountd 导出列表过长致权限绕过漏洞","description":"SunOS/Solaris 系统中 NFS mount 守护进程存在访问控制绕过漏洞。当 NFS 导出列表条目超过 256 字符时，守护进程未能正确处理超长字符串，导致所有访问控制检查失效。远程攻击者无需任何身份认证即可挂载本应受限的 NFS 目录，从而非法访问敏感文件。该漏洞影响 SunOS 4.x 及 Solaris 早期版本，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0211"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1994-02-14T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:55.270","remediation":"安装 Sun 针对对应操作系统版本的安全补丁：SunOS 4.1.3/4.1.3_U1 安装补丁 101945-xx，Solaris 2.3 安装补丁 101358-xx，Solaris 2.4 安装补丁 101945-xx。无法立即打补丁时，将 /etc/exports 中每条导出条目控制在 256 字符以内，使用主机名/IP 而非 netgroup 进行访问控制，并在 NFS 服务端防火墙限制仅允许可信网络访问 portmap（111/tcp,111/udp）和 nfsd（2049/tcp,2049/udp）。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/24","https://vuls.cert.org/confluence/pages/viewpage.action?pageId=96665790","https://vuls.cert.org/confluence/pages/viewpage.action?pageId=97124517","https://vuls.cert.org/confluence/pages/viewpage.action?pageId=97124527"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0397.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1422","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1422.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1242","title":"HP HP-UX subnetconfig 本地权限提升漏洞","description":"HP-UX 9.01 及 9.0 版本中的 subnetconfig 组件存在权限提升漏洞。本地攻击者在已获取系统普通账户访问权限的条件下，可通过利用 subnetconfig 对输入参数处理不当的缺陷，以 root 权限执行任意命令，从而实现本地提权。该漏洞无法远程利用，仅限本地攻击，攻击者需具有系统本地账户方可利用。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1242"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1994-02-07T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:01.277","remediation":"升级 HP-UX 至 10.x 或更新的受支持版本，或移除 `subnetconfig` 的 setuid 权限位：`chmod u-s /usr/sbin/subnetconfig`。限制不可信用户的本地登录权限，并审核 `/etc/passwd` 中可登录用户列表。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://packetstormsecurity.org/advisories/hpalert/003","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/2162","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/b4f1378756fd26f414d09a97dc81126672830951/1999/CVE-1999-1242.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/7481e97cf7b60a5b982d99d7dad1ea61174940fb/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1242.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1242","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/c1321b1a6b0cb3a4c18f791e2c8443742c0cb0b0/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1242.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-1242.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/cdfc8886d71af7ef3bdab3e4db46753ff8af6538/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-g6hx-v77f-92pc/GHSA-g6hx-v77f-92pc.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x88000/87846/info.html","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1242.json","https://github.com/Yuning-J/VulnerabilityClassifier/blob/c0f06c21b73c26b5ee2b75c21a498eb04eada4b5/threatPrediction/cveIDThreatType/cve_idgainpre","https://github.com/hungryfoolou/Vulnerability_Mining/blob/3df1d8ed0489ae1228f975ae1f58a690aae53886/craw/cveid_craw/cveid_craw/data/cveid_by_kind/cveid_gainpre.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1422.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0362","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0362.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0181","title":"Unix rpc.walld 远程命令执行漏洞","description":"rpc.walld（wall daemon）是 Unix 系统中用于向所有在线终端广播消息的 RPC 服务，默认通过 rpc 协议监听网络请求。该服务存在访问控制缺陷，未授权远程攻击者无需认证即可向其发送特制 RPC 请求，向所有登录用户终端广播虚假消息，导致拒绝服务或社会工程攻击。部分实现中攻击者还可利用调试功能或命令行注入执行任意远程命令。该漏洞影响 Solaris、HP-UX 等 Unix 系统。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":6.8,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0181"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1994-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:46.403","remediation":"禁用 rpc.walld 服务（如不需全局广播功能），或通过 tcpwrappers 在 /etc/hosts.deny 添加 `walld: ALL` 限制访问来源。各 UNIX 厂商（如 Sun、HP、IBM）曾发布对应补丁，建议查阅原厂安全公告获取对应修复包。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0181"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0362.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0550","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0550.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0334","title":"Sun Solaris fsck 本地权限提升漏洞","description":"Solaris 2.2 和 2.3 系统中，fsck（文件系统一致性检查）在系统启动过程中执行失败后，系统会降级至单用户维护模式，此时拥有物理访问权限的本地用户无需认证即可直接获取 root shell 权限。该漏洞属于本地权限提升漏洞，攻击者须具备物理接触目标主机的条件，通过在系统引导阶段触发 fsck 检查失败来利用此问题，进而完全控制受影响系统。该漏洞 CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高，影响 Solaris 2.2 及 2.3 版本。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0334"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1993-12-16T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:10.570","remediation":"升级到 Solaris 2.4 或更高版本，该漏洞已在后续版本中修复。如无法升级，应限制物理访问，确保控制台仅授权人员可用，并在系统启动时值守以防止 fsck 被交互式劫持。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0334"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0550.toml"}]